{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<xsl:copy-of>","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/copy-of","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>&lt;xsl:copy-of&gt;</code> 要素は、select 属性が出力文書に指定するものすべての深いコピー (子孫ノードを含む) を作成します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;xsl:copy-of select=EXPRESSION /&gt; </pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"required_attributes","title":"必須属性","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"select\"><code>select</code></dt>\n <dd>何をコピーするかを指定する XPath 式を使用します。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"optional_attributes","title":"任意属性","isH3":true,"content":"<p>なし</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"type","title":"タイプ","isH3":true,"content":"<p>命令は、テンプレート内に表示されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p>XSLT, section 11.3.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko のサポート","isH3":true,"content":"<p>サポート済み</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"<xsl:copy-of> 要素は、select 属性が出力文書に指定するものすべての深いコピー (子孫ノードを含む) を作成します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<xsl:copy-of>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"copy-of","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"copy-of","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"copy-of","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"copy-of","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"fold